.Dd August 3, 2017
.Dt UHCI 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm uhci
.Nd UHCI USB Host Controller driver
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "device uhci"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for UHCI-type PCI based USB controllers.
.Sh HARDWARE
The
.Nm
driver supports all UHCI v1.1 compliant controllers including:
.Pp
.Bl -bullet -compact
.It
Intel 82371AB/EB (PIIX4)
.It
Intel 82371SB (PIIX3)
.It
VIA 83C572
.El
.Sh MIB Variables
The
.Nm
driver exposes the following variables in the
.Va hw.usb.uhci
branch of the
.Xr sysctl 3
MIB:
.Bl -tag -width ".Va debug"
.It Va debug
Debug output level, where 0 is debugging disabled and larger values increase
debug message verbosity.
Default is 0.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr ehci 4 ,
.Xr ohci 4 ,
.Xr xhci 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
device driver first appeared in
.Fx 3.0 .
